    "body_html": "<p>Pair of 316 marine-grade stainless steel mounting legs and bases for installing SeaKing bait boards on Australian fishing vessels.</p>\n<h3>Specifications</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<strong>Material:</strong> 316 marine-grade stainless steel</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Compatibility:</strong> Universal — fits all SeaKing bait board models</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Includes:</strong> Pair of legs + 2 base brackets + mounting hardware</li>\n<li>\n<strong>Finish:</strong> Mirror-polished, salt-corrosion resistant</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Shipping &amp; warranty</h3>\n<p>Free Australia-wide shipping. 1-year manufacturer warranty.</p>",
